A em conjunto com Prestador de Servi&ccedil;os Tecnol&oacute;gicos, estes ficar&atilde;o impedidos de demandar servi&ccedil;os no SGTEC pelo prazo de at&eacute; dois anos, al&eacute;m de outras medidas judiciais cab&iacute;veis que o SEBRAE/BA entenda pertinente.</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;background:#4F81BD;mso-background-themecolor:\r\naccent1\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">CL&Aacute;USULA</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> <span style=\"color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">QUARTA</span> <span style=\"color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">&ndash; DA DEN&Uacute;NCIA</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">&Eacute; permitido a ambas as partes denunciar o contrato, desde que de forma motivada, neste caso dever&aacute; haver devolu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos recursos de forma proporcional aos servi&ccedil;os j&aacute; executados.</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;background:#4F81BD;mso-background-themecolor:\r\naccent1\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">CL&Aacute;USULA</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> <span style=\"color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">QUINTA</span> <span style=\"color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">&ndash; DA MORA</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Em caso de mora no cumprimento das obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es, haver&aacute; incid&ecirc;ncia de multa de 2% no vencimento e 1% ao m&ecirc;s.</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n<o:RelyOnVML />\r\n<o:AllowPNG />\r\n</o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;background:#4F81BD;mso-background-themecolor:\r\naccent1\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">CL&Aacute;USULA</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> <span style=\"color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">SEXTA</span> <span style=\"color:white;mso-themecolor:background1\">&ndash;<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>TERMO DE AUTORIZA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DE DEVOLU&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n#nome_responsavel#, nacionalidade____________________ , estado civil__________________ , profiss&atilde;o ________________ , inscrito no #cpf#, autoriza o Servi&ccedil;o de Apoio &agrave;s Micro e Pequenas Empresas Bahia, a efetuar o dep&oacute;sito banc&aacute;rio, referente a eventual devolu&ccedil;&atilde;o, na conta descrita abaixo:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n#devolucao#\r\n<table style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"background:#4f81bd; color: white; font-weight: bold; text-align: left;\">\r\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #4f81bd\">CL&Aacute;USULA&nbsp; S&Eacute;TIMA &ndash; DO FORO</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Fica estabelecido entre as partes que o foro competente para a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o de qualquer lit&iacute;gio decorrente deste contrato &eacute; o de Salvador-BA, exclu&iacute;do qualquer outro.</p>\r\n<p>E, por assim terem acordado, assinam este Termo de Ades&atilde;o e Compromisso, em tr&ecirc;s vias de igual teor e forma.</p>\r\n<table style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n            <p>#cidade_assinatura#, &nbsp;#data_assinatura#&nbsp; de &nbsp;#mes_assinatura#&nbsp; de &nbsp;#ano_assinatura#&nbsp;.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style=\"margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 50px\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 45%; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid black; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 5px;\">#nome_responsavel#<br />\r\n            RESPONSAVEL PELA #razao_social#</td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 10%; vertical-align: top;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 45%; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid black; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 5px;\">\r\n            <p>RESPONS&Aacute;VEL PELO ATENDIMENTO &ndash; SEBRAE/BA<br />\r\n            (N&atilde;o rubricar)</p>\r\n            <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pir.ba.sebrae.com.br/sebrae_grc/admin/fckupload/images/ASSINATURA%20ADHVAN.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"66\" /></td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://pir.ba.sebrae.com.br/sebrae_grc/admin/fckupload/images/ASSINATURA%20FRANKLIN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"110\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center;\">#diretor_superintendente#<br />\r\n            Diretor Superintendente</td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center;\">#diretor_atendimento#<br />\r\n            Diretor de Atendimento</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>' WHERE `codigo`='evento_modelo_contrato_sg_cont';

